### Auto-Enrollment API Tests

### 1. Preview Auto-Enrollment (see what would happen without actually enrolling)
GET http://localhost:8088/api/v1/enrollments/auto-enroll/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Auto-Enroll All Students
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/enrollments/auto-enroll
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Auto-Enroll Students by Grade Level (Elementary)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/enrollments/auto-enroll/grade/ELEMENTARY
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Auto-Enroll Students by Grade Level (High School)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/enrollments/auto-enroll/grade/HIGH
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get All Enrollments to verify results
GET http://localhost:8088/api/v1/enrollments?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get All Classes to see created classes
GET http://localhost:8088/api/v1/classes?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
